</TEXT_BULLETS>
<TEXT_BULLETS item="y">
<Topic>Compressed encrypted files</Topic>
<Text>Fixed problems with files set to both compressed and encrypted modes.  But note that compressing an encrypted file still does not significantly reduce its size.</Text>
