<Text>This is an unstable development snapshot.  It is nearly ready to become a stable release, but it could still contain bugs.  Testing and bug reports are appreciated.</Text>
</TEXT_BULLETS>
<TEXT_BULLETS item="y">
<Topic>Missing features</Topic>
<Text>The French translation of the GUI is the only one completed so far.  None of the documentation translations  have been updated.</Text>
</TEXT_BULLETS>
<TEXT_BULLETS item="y">
<Topic>Qt4 required</Topic>
